Independently implemented from a clean-room multi-provider architecture design.
General concept (unified Chinese financial data MCP with provider fallback)
inspired by:
  - zlinzzzz/finData-mcp-server (https://github.com/zlinzzzz/finData-mcp-server)
  - guangxiangdebizi/FinanceMCP (https://github.com/guangxiangdebizi/FinanceMCP)
  - guangxiangdebizi/FinanceMCP-DCTHS (https://github.com/guangxiangdebizi/FinanceMCP-DCTHS)

No source code was copied. Wind / iFinD / Choice integrations are intentionally
left as skeletons because they require commercial terminal licenses; users must
follow respective vendor terms when implementing.
